ass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佛教=食齋+拜佛像+積陰德=道教"},{"pid":"920bbfc441ac5eff1d1124515f3fe4d111eecbcd","tid":227031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:47:24.000Z","msg":"其實係好多人混水搵食"},{"pid":"0c685cb73ad82fb6df16eaaee3b17a8b4f4d884d","tid":227031,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本唔關宗唔宗教事 係d人太蠢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佛教7就唔關宗教事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個龍門有幾大"},{"pid":"2da24ef0f340fd3dc2e0bfda82345e1053412f19","tid":227031,"uid":100809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"佢地係信佛，但唔係修佛<br />\n唔去修行，剩係諗住拜神燒香放生就可以去極樂世界<br />\n太天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90906c813fdeec3fd1ff6189ecf7c6f2bb6f46a","tid":227031,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>根本唔關宗唔宗教事 係d人太蠢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佛教7就唔關宗教事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個龍門有幾大</blockquote><br />\n佛教未又係同耶教一樣性質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前者主張輪迴因果報應, 後者講上帝審判你<br />\n未又係講緊一樣superpower去主宰你既生命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n耶撚之所以更加黑人憎,只因為佢地排他性更強, 而佛教冇咁強, 中國傳統主張謙遜<br />\n<br />\n講到尾D宗教黎黎去去未又係咁既本質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58ec55165b19b2b11a8ae3cc4a21481c7e71eea","tid":227031,"uid":91982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:52:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfdfc82f8270b8a9f2c71bbe12b643c2ec951d68","tid":227031,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:53:37.000Z","msg":"放生呢個行為本身就戇鳩,特登捉鳩左d魚然後放撚左佢話積德,虛偽到極點"},{"pid":"39b0ff0dacc172aad6584145e299c67472a60467","tid":227031,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:57:02.000Z","msg":"成日覺得放生呢個行為好反智 真係唔想殺生就戒肉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懶有善心咁用好多錢買好多海鮮放生 但轉個頭就大魚大肉<br />\n根本呢班人都自我感覺良好 喺度自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3537f513396bcb17701b35f25dde3076854defb7","tid":227031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:00:02.000Z","msg":"撈魚童：上次有龍蝦<br />\n其中一名年僅12歲的男童自稱家人是大澳漁民，發現放生的都是養魚，因知青衣碼頭是放生熱點，所以常來等候捉魚回家加餸，「最緊要知佢下次幾時再放」。他更說：「上次有龍蝦，但好難撈，只係撈到3條紅鮋。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n告訴我其實佢 原來曾放了蝦"},{"pid":"5c6d2fc280388a81fc3cc4187652d62cab7dccec","tid":227031,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撈魚童：上次有龍蝦<br />\n其中一名年僅12歲的男童自稱家人是大澳漁民，發現放生的都是養魚，因知青衣碼頭是放生熱點，所以常來等候捉魚回家加餸，「最緊要知佢下次幾時再放」。他更說：「上次有龍蝦，但好難撈，只係撈到3條紅鮋。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n告訴我其實佢 原來曾放了蝦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490052d433bb690f3259dac6d061617e91663ca4","tid":227031,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>班宗教撚係咪弱智</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nd 阿姑會講： 我成日去圓玄學院食齋同黃大仙，我信佛嫁！<br />\n<br />\n我會唔出聲，行開算..</blockquote><br />\n咁去荃灣食齋方便過大嶼山好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黃大仙拜神都係貪就腳<br />\n根本好多香港人都信佛道兩教</blockquote><br />\n其實係佢地自己都未分得清咩係佛咩係道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佛教=食齋+拜佛像+積陰德=道教</blockquote><br />\n東方人(特別嶺南人)信宗教有樣好嘅，就係乜撚都拜，滿天神佛，都唔知拜緊乜，迷迷糊糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(耶撚，muslim就係有排外性質，一旦拜左某個神就其他都係假神，所以就成日打晒架)"},{"pid":"a77b32d03584cb24b442d89501169d9896d56718","tid":227031,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地係信佛，但唔係修佛<br />\n唔去修行，剩係諗住拜神燒香放生就可以去極樂世界<br />\n太天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地係諗住下世輪迴做有錢佬，唔係去極樂"},{"pid":"ea0dacba1f00c3c9050579200ad2386e1ebb5868","tid":227031,"uid":22959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:18:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日覺得放生呢個行為好反智 真係唔想殺生就戒肉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懶有善心咁用好多錢買好多海鮮放生 但轉個頭就大魚大肉<br />\n根本呢班人都自我感覺良好 喺度自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而且佢地買完呢條魚 d 漁民又唔係唔再捉魚 只會繼續捉其他魚去賣<br />\n放左呢條魚 但係就由其他魚代替呢條魚放係魚市場入面 變相根本冇做過d 咩「積陰德」嘅野 <br />\n一個唔小心放錯d 淡水魚落海 累死條魚 作嘅孽仲多一重添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16925adf0be68bb31f38b831692f236ee832a40","tid":227031,"uid":103936,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根本唔關宗唔宗教事 係d人太蠢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佛教7就唔關宗教事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個龍門有幾大</blockquote><br />\n佛教未又係同耶教一樣性質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前者主張輪迴因果報應, 後者講上帝審判你<br />\n未又係講緊一樣superpower去主宰你既生命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n耶撚之所以更加黑人憎,只因為佢地排他性更強, 而佛教冇咁強, 中國傳統主張謙遜<br />\n<br />\n講到尾D宗教黎黎去去未又係咁既本質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你要明白每個宗教都會有人 借教義搵水魚<br />\n與其屌宗教 不如屌搵人笨柒同被搵笨柒果個<br />\n畢竟樹大有枯枝 人多有白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4151f92a67873b0ccc9e05abe3860f801aff2c9","tid":227031,"uid":48631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日覺得放生呢個行為好反智 真係唔想殺生就戒肉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懶有善心咁用好多錢買好多海鮮放生 但轉個頭就大魚大肉<br />\n根本呢班人都自我感覺良好 喺度自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而且佢地買完呢條魚 d 漁民又唔係唔再捉魚 只會繼續捉其他魚去賣<br />\n放左呢條魚 但係就由其他魚代替呢條魚放係魚市場入面 變相根本冇做過d 咩「積陰德」嘅野 <br />\n一個唔小心放錯d 淡水魚落海 累死條魚 作嘅孽仲多一重添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基於demand and supply,越多人放生漁民只會捉越多魚tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d8298dde13309cfd1d7545f2334874e6c23b8f","tid":227031,"uid":22959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:42:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日覺得放生呢個行為好反智 真係唔想殺生就戒肉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懶有善心咁用好多錢買好多海鮮放生 但轉個頭就大魚大肉<br />\n根本呢班人都自我感覺良好 喺度自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而且佢地買完呢條魚 d 漁民又唔係唔再捉魚 只會繼續捉其他魚去賣<br />\n放左呢條魚 但係就由其他魚代替呢條魚放係魚市場入面 變相根本冇做過d 咩「積陰德」嘅野 <br />\n一個唔小心放錯d 淡水魚落海 累死條魚 作嘅孽仲多一重添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基於demand and supply,越多人放生漁民只會捉越多魚tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以放生真係好撚on9"},{"pid":"8c66320a79a89613db495c4e0b5ff9cfb2f7d2dc","tid":227031,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"其實如果係被人捉去食，咁不如由得佢嚮個魚市場俾人買仲好啦，對條魚個分別只係死之前有得出黎遊玩下"},{"pid":"f3765a55a1ca2c4ff9653950da11948f5000d1d8","tid":227031,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"屌那星d外來物種咪殺哂d本地種囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9593ee12c6e235148b3811922b429138e3e4c61c","tid":227031,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本好多香港人做所謂善事同捐錢個心態就係想積陰德希望自己生活會好啲,完全唔係真心想幫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁捐錢起碼都叫真係幫到人嘅, 做善事之前唔使寫份personal statement等審評啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c845af8c1790de0daf16dc55df6df26b96eee848","tid":227031,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日覺得放生呢個行為好反智 真係唔想殺生就戒肉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懶有善心咁用好多錢買好多海鮮放生 但轉個頭就大魚大肉<br />\n根本呢班人都自我感覺良好 喺度自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而且佢地買完呢條魚 d 漁民又唔係唔再捉魚 只會繼續捉其他魚去賣<br />\n放左呢條魚 但係就由其他魚代替呢條魚放係魚市場入面 變相根本冇做過d 咩「積陰德」嘅野 <br />\n一個唔小心放錯d 淡水魚落海 累死條魚 作嘅孽仲多一重添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基於demand and supply,越多人放生漁民只會捉越多魚tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔到咩demand and supply話事，天然資源唔係你話提升supply就提升，其實個海已經冇乜魚捉，我老豆成日去買魚同啲魚販傾計，佢地成日呻來貨越來越少，佢地都得出一個結論，中國人口太多，海入面啲魚已經接近捉晒食晒"},{"pid":"16031ee822df93434bdf6d2b9ece02e0e5cd6240","tid":227031,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:55:25.000Z","msg":"北角碼頭果間海鮮檔咪又係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放生完捉返上黎放鋪頭又買過"},{"pid":"10e0ffa93aa798d78e28c67080046ce0cdeff566","tid":227031,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根本唔關宗唔宗教事 係d人太蠢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佛教7就唔關宗教事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個龍門有幾大</blockquote><br />\n佛教未又係同耶教一樣性質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前者主張輪迴因果報應, 後者講上帝審判你<br />\n未又係講緊一樣superpower去主宰你既生命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n耶撚之所以更加黑人憎,只因為佢地排他性更強, 而佛教冇咁強, 中國傳統主張謙遜<br />\n<br />\n講到尾D宗教黎黎去去未又係咁既本質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你要明白每個宗教都會有人 借教義搵水魚<br />\n與其屌宗教 不如屌搵人笨柒同被搵笨柒果個<br />\n畢竟樹大有枯枝 人多有白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最慘就係宗教既特質就係麻目人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令佢地唔再理性思考, 雖然我唔排除信徒入面都會有理性既人,<br />\n不過好多都係盲從既垃圾信徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d55a712adbc7581dfc10b052418036d82f59e51","tid":227031,"uid":56063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"放生只係自我感覺良好&hellip;"},{"pid":"4782c1cf8a4cbb1e7d243acde564a4908ccef31c","tid":227031,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"亂咁放生會破壞生態平衡架"},{"pid":"91960edcc5f86a1882a3e298c288560478e0f62b","tid":227031,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"佛撚戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a11ad355f3994c660f19412dc1c96c130b380a3","tid":227031,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"成班信佛既偽善者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜都唔識<br />\n見識游水就掉落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd7a68c0af001fcd3edb6bc3f5c4f10216caf3a","tid":227031,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:10:36.000Z","msg":"白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9d856ebdc1ee8f5dd3e89471e9131900154b8c","tid":227031,"uid":91227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:26:16.000Z","msg":"信佛放生其實同偽善冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b28063ad7661d5d268e821559b02a622f38c677","tid":227031,"uid":45848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:26:42.000Z","msg":"佢地班人影衰晒佛教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到佢地又要報名費又特登坐遊艇，可能借宗教名抽油水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee742a1aa2a86ed6967bfc311e9bbf361c68816","tid":227031,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>撈魚童：上次有龍蝦<br />\n其中一名年僅12歲的男童自稱家人是大澳漁民，發現放生的都是養魚，因知青衣碼頭是放生熱點，所以常來等候捉魚回家加餸，「最緊要知佢下次幾時再放」。他更說：「上次有龍蝦，但好難撈，只係撈到3條紅鮋。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n告訴我其實佢 原來曾放了蝦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59947ce3b5d8e7d50258b0ac40c4a391c77037b","tid":227031,"uid":104088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:30:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e395c1e9e7a2253c26da1b65a19d58d9b61aefd5","tid":227031,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:35:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"019dec2af69eb38f0c31baae377e05a1cdd6041c","tid":227031,"uid":53011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"成件事好on9<br />\n班on9善信扮晒有愛心 偽善<br />\n宗教團體志在捐款<br />\n班垃圾港猪去執人著數<br />\n<br />\n香港地真係痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435fbf6db10ad973a04d2a0709acb26f39b69bf2","tid":227031,"uid":70928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:48:12.000Z","msg":"痴撚線釣客"},{"pid":"2351ed725544e8a42a4eb52ff08cd98d4c2f7f7f","tid":227031,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實信佛是好，起碼好過信耶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢D放生行為... 唔好拎D動物條命黎玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 荃灣海面，頂你之前去荃灣海邊跑步個海臭到仆街，你放野落海咪即係殺咗佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無知真係好可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩邊都唔信<blockquote><blockquote>引用</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n但年年都見信佛既人響到挑戰人類智商下限<br />\n除左同情d海鮮外 真心諗究竟係d人信佛信到蠢曬定係淨係得d蠢人先會信佛<br />\n究竟仲有邊間佛寺係為左普渡眾生而唔係響到做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9269cdc0cc0864e114df4d9ba7503a9ad61bc9","tid":227031,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>班宗教撚係咪弱智</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nd 阿姑會講： 我成日去圓玄學院食齋同黃大仙，我信佛嫁！<br />\n<br />\n我會唔出聲，行開算..</blockquote><br />\n咁去荃灣食齋方便過大嶼山好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黃大仙拜神都係貪就腳<br />\n根本好多香港人都信佛道兩教</blockquote><br />\n其實係佢地自己都未分得清咩係佛咩係道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佛教=食齋+拜佛像+積陰德=道教</blockquote><br />\n東方人(特別嶺南人)信宗教有樣好嘅，就係乜撚都拜，滿天神佛，都唔知拜緊乜，迷迷糊糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(耶撚，muslim就係有排外性質，一旦拜左某個神就其他都係假神，所以就成日打晒架)</blockquote><br />\n其實華人係無神論，因為佢地唔係真係信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09fca609e35712f54d42737c31233f636b3fae1f","tid":227031,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim